// LoF/DoS sweep (cron135): the old-reserve proof for UpdateBaseUnitMints must also reject
// frozen canonical reserves. A frozen empty reserve is not a usable clean custody rail; accepting it
// during a mint reset can hide an unserviceable retired reserve behind the new base-unit config.
